EDUCATIONAL USE

This project was created for educational purposes as part of the Database 
Management Systems (DBMS) course at Bahria University. It demonstrates 
practical implementation of DBMS concepts including database design, 
normalization, ACID transactions, and SQL operations.

For academic use, proper attribution to the project and team members is 
appreciated but not strictly required.
